(Think of your wallet like a big toy factory with one master recipe card.) Tj
T*
(- Your **mnemonic words** are that recipe card.) Tj
T*
(- The wallet uses the recipe card to make one giant secret dough called the **seed**.) Tj
T*
(- From that seed, the wallet bakes two different toy families:) Tj
T*
(- **Falcon toys**: used to prove "this is really me" \(signatures\).) Tj
T*
(- **Kyber toys**: used to lock and unlock secret messages \(private payload encryption\).) Tj
T*
(- Then the wallet makes addresses from those toys:) Tj
T*
(- payment address \(public receive/spend\),) Tj
T*
(- private bundle identity \(X-address\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(If you keep the recipe card \(mnemonic\) and the same options \(passphrase, account/index/role) Tj
T*
(path\), the factory can rebuild the same toy family again.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(That is deterministic recovery.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
